author: johnh
msg: Small updates to RMR enabling it to work on other browsers (eg. for use in parent verifiability in the future):
* wrap channelWindow assignment to ensure no permissions exceptions prevent RMR setup
* attach onresize handler through attachEvent if present, enabling RMR to work on IE (if the relay exists; 404s will still not work)
Thanks to Zhen Huang for the research and code.
